 NATIONAL 2|publisher=nimes-olympique.com||accessdate=4 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=GK|name=C\u00f4me Charrier}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=GK|name=[[Valentin Rabouille]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=Alexandre Ferreira}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=J\u00e9r\u00e9my Iafrate}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=Enzo Fontanelli}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=Mat\u00e9o Maillefaud}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=Julien Megier}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=DF|name=Micka\u00ebl Gas}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Kl\u00e9ri Serber}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=[[Matt\u00e9o Ahlinvi]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Simon Calancha}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Nacim El Hassani}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Quentin Gregorio}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=FW|name=Luca Valls}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=FW|name=Axel Urie}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=FW|name=Timothy Cardona}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Hugo Huriez}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=FRA|pos=MF|name=Houssine Labiad}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=FRA|name=[[Th\u00e9o Sainte-Luce]]|pos=DF|other=on loan to [[Gaz\u00e9lec Ajaccio|Gaz\u00e9lec]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Notable players===\nBelow are the notable former players who have represented N\u00eemes in [[Ligue 1|league]] and international competition since the club's foundation in 1937. To appear in the section below, a player must have played in at least 80 official matches for the club or represented the national team for which the player is eligible during his stint with N\u00eemes or following his departure. \n\n''For a complete list of N\u00eemes Olympique players, see [[:Category:N\u00eemes Olympique players]]''\n\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em| \n'''{{flag|France}}'''\n* [[Jean-Pierre Adams]]\n* [[William Ayache]]\n* [[Ivan Bek]]\n* [[Pierre Bernard (footballer)|Pierre Bernard]]\n* [[Laurent Blanc]]\n* [[Bernard Boissier]]\n* [[\u00c9ric Cantona]]\n* [[Andr\u00e9 Chardar]]\n* [[Johann Charpenet]]\n* [[Paul Chillan]]\n* [[Patrick Cubaynes]]\n* [[Johnny Ecker]]\n* [[Jean-Marc Ferratge]]\n* [[Kader Firoud]]\n* [[Ren\u00e9 Girard (footballer)|Ren\u00e9 Girard]]\n* [[Edmond Haan]]\n* [[Mahi Khennane]]\n* [[Maurice Lafont]]\n* [[Michel M\u00e9zy]]\n* [[Jacky Novi]]\n* [[Christian Perez (footballer born 1963)|Christian Perez]]\n* [[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Piquionne]]\n* [[Beno\u00eet Poulain]]\n* [[Bernard Rahis]]\n* [[Henri Skiba]]\n* [[Joseph Ujlaki]]\n* [[Philippe Vercruysse]]\n* [[Jacques Vergnes|Jacky Vergnes]]\n* [[Alexandre Villaplane]]\n* [[Anthony Vosalho|Anthony Vosahlo]]\n'''{{flag|Algeria}}'''\n* [[Omar Belbey]]\n* [[Ali Boulebda]]\n* [[Rabah Gamouh]]\n* [[Mahi Khennane]]\n* [[Faouzi Mansouri]]\n* [[Djamel Menad]]\n* [[Mehdi Mostefa]]\n* [[Abder Ramdane]]\n* [[Amokrane Oualiken]]\n* [[Abderraouf Zarabi]]\n'''{{flag|Argentina}}'''\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Cuciuffo]]\n* [[Jorge Dom\u00ednguez (footballer)]]\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Daniel Ponce]]\n'''{{flag|Austria}}'''\n* [[Heinz Schilcher]]\n'''{{flag|Belgium}}'''\n* [[Roger Van Gool]]\n'''{{flag|Benin}}'''\n* [[Mouritala Ogunbiyi]]\n* [[Steve Mouni\u00e9]]\n'''{{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}'''\n* [[Mehmed Ba\u017edarevi\u0107]]\n'''{{flag|Burkina Faso}}'''\n* [[Issouf Ouattara]]\n'''{{flag|Cameroon}}'''\n* [[Benjamin Moukandjo]]\n'''{{flag|Central African Republic}}'''\n* [[Eloge Enza Yamissi|Eloge Enza-Yamissi]]\n* [[Manass\u00e9 Enza-Yamissi]]\n'''{{flag|Comoros}}'''\n* [[Mohamed M'Changama]]\n'''{{flag|C\u00f4te d'Ivoire}}'''\n* [[Guy Demel]]\n'''{{flag|Croatia}}'''\n* [[Darko Vuki\u0107]]\n'''{{flag|Czechoslovakia}}'''\n* [[Adolf Scherer]]\n* [[Du\u0161an Tittel]]\n'''{{flag|Democratic Republic of Congo}}'''\n* [[Alain Masudi]]\n'''{{flag|Denmark}}'''\n* [[Kristen Nygaard (footballer)|Kristen Nygaard]]\n'''{{flag|Ghana}}'''\n* [[Arthur Moses]]\n'''{{flag|Hungary}}'''\n* [[Vilmos Kohu