b's foundation in 1937. To appear in the section below, a player must have played in at least 80 official matches for the club or represented the national team for which the player is eligible during his stint with N\u00eemes or following his departure. \n\n''For a complete list of N\u00eemes Olympique players, see [[:Category:N\u00eemes Olympique players]]''\n\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em| \n'''{{flag|France}}'''\n* [[Jean-Pierre Adams]]\n* [[William Ayache]]\n* [[Ivan Bek]]\n* [[Pierre Bernard (footballer)|Pierre Bernard]]\n* [[Laurent Blanc]]\n* [[Bernard Boissier]]\n* [[\u00c9ric Cantona]]\n* [[Andr\u00e9 Chardar]]\n* [[Johann Charpenet]]\n* [[Paul Chillan]]\n* [[Patrick Cubaynes]]\n* [[Johnny Ecker]]\n* [[Jean-Marc Ferratge]]\n* [[Kader Firoud]]\n* [[Ren\u00e9 Girard (footballer)|Ren\u00e9 Girard]]\n* [[Edmond Haan]]\n* [[Mahi Khennane]]\n* [[Maurice Lafont]]\n* [[Michel M\u00e9zy]]\n* [[Jacky Novi]]\n* [[Christian Perez (footballer born 1963)|Christian Perez]]\n* [[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Piquionne]]\n* [[Beno\u00eet Poulain]]\n* [[Bernard Rahis]]\n* [[Henri Skiba]]\n* [[Joseph Ujlaki]]\n* [[Philippe Vercruysse]]\n* [[Jacques Vergnes|Jacky Vergnes]]\n* [[Alexandre Villaplane]]\n* [[Anthony Vosalho|Anthony Vosahlo]]\n'''{{flag|Algeria}}'''\n* [[Omar Belbey]]\n* [[Ali Boulebda]]\n* [[Rabah Gamouh]]\n* [[Mahi Khennane]]\n* [[Faouzi Mansouri]]\n* [[Djamel Menad]]\n* [[Mehdi Mostefa]]\n* [[Abder Ramdane]]\n* [[Amokrane Oualiken]]\n* [[Abderraouf Zarabi]]\n'''{{flag|Argentina}}'''\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Cuciuffo]]\n* [[Jorge Dom\u00ednguez (footballer)]]\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Daniel Ponce]]\n'''{{flag|Austria}}'''\n* [[Heinz Schilcher]]\n'''{{flag|Belgium}}'''\n* [[Roger Van Gool]]\n'''{{flag|Benin}}'''\n* [[Mouritala Ogunbiyi]]\n* [[Steve Mouni\u00e9]]\n'''{{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}'''\n* [[Mehmed Ba\u017edarevi\u0107]]\n'''{{flag|Burkina Faso}}'''\n* [[Issouf Ouattara]]\n'''{{flag|Cameroon}}'''\n* [[Benjamin Moukandjo]]\n'''{{flag|Central African Republic}}'''\n* [[Eloge E